name: caniuse-lite
description: A smaller version of caniuse-db, with only the essentials!

scripts.prepublish: rm -Rf dist && mkdir -p dist/unpacker && mkdir -p dist/lib && cp -R src/unpacker/* dist/unpacker/ && cp src/lib/statuses.js dist/lib/statuses.js && cp src/lib/supported.js dist/lib/supported.js
